name: Vatova A., 1935. The fishery grounds near Alexandria, II. A bottom sample taken at Alexandria, Notes and Memoirs No 9. Fisheries Research Directorate, Egypt
description: This is a historical report, publishedin 1935 by A. Vatova. It contains specific information about a bottom sample that was taken once in the eastern harbour of Alexandria, nearthe Marine Laboratory during the floristical and faunistical survey of Adolf Steueron the coasts near Alexandria mainly with the vessel "El Hoot".
